return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2025-06-12 06:10:10+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Plugins - Featured Image from URL (FIFU) - Stable (latest release)','language'=>'ko_KR','messages'=>['Photo credit'=>'사진 크레딧','When FIFU imports an image URL from the search engine, it also retrieves the address of the remote post that owns the image. By enabling \'Settings → Image → Page Redirection\', FIFU adds a link to the image when it’s displayed on singular posts of your site. Then, by clicking on the image, the visitor is redirected to the remote post. This is FIFU’s way of giving credit to the author, since the search engine may include copyrighted images in the results.
